    "description": "Are you a skilled Backend Developer looking for your next big career move? CDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd in Bhopal offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout CDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nCDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with CDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
